  "content": {
    "prompt": "<div><div class=\"stimulus_reference\"><div class=\"standalone_image\"><img alt=\"The figure shows two positions of a disk between a ceiling and a floor. Position A is labeled Released from Rest, and it shows the disk high above the floor and suspended from a string that is attached to the ceiling. Position B is labeled Just Before Hitting the Floor, and it shows the disk slightly above the floor after some of the string is unwrapped.&nbsp;\" src=\"/images/8d2a80234c830b043f9ce96b131bc20f.svg\"></div></div></div><p class=\"stem_paragraph\">One end of a string of negligible mass is wrapped around a disk and the other end is attached to a ceiling, as shown. The disk is released from rest at position <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"A\"><math alttext=\"A\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mtext>A</mtext></math></span></span> and the string does not slip on the disk. When the&nbsp;disk reaches position <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"B\"><math alttext=\"B\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mtext>B</mtext></math></span></span>, the absolute value of the change in the gravitational potential energy of the disk‑Earth system is <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"delta U\"><math alttext=\"delta U\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mtext>Δ</mtext><mi>U</mi></math></span></span>. Which of the following correctly compares the total kinetic energy and the rotational kinetic energy of the disk to <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"delta U\"><math alttext=\"delta U\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mtext>Δ</mtext><mi>U</mi></math></span></span> ?</p><div class=\"table_wrapper\"><table class=\"tgroup align:center cols:3 colsep:0 frame:none rowsep:0\"><colgroup><col class=\"colspec align:center colname:col1 colnum:1 colsep:1 colwidth:50\"><col class=\"colspec align:center colname:col2 colnum:2 colwidth:50\"><col class=\"colspec align:center colname:col3 colnum:3 colwidth:50\"></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\"><tr class=\"row rowsep:1\"><th class=\"entry colname:col1\"></th><th class=\"entry colname:col2\">Total Kinetic Energy</th><th class=\"entry colname:col3\">Rotational Kinetic Energy</th></tr></thead><tbody class=\"tbody valign:middle\"><tr class=\"row\"><td class=\"entry colname:col1\">A</td><td class=\"entry colname:col2\">Equal to <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"delta U\"><math alttext=\"delta U\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mtext>Δ</mtext><mi>U</mi></math></span></span></td><td class=\"entry colname:col3\">Equal to <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"delta U\"><math alttext=\"delta U\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mtext>Δ</mtext><mi>U</mi></math></span></span></td></tr><tr class=\"row\"><td class=\"entry colname:col1\">B</td><td class=\"entry colname:col2\">Equal to <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"delta U\"><math alttext=\"delta U\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mtext>Δ</mtext><mi>U</mi></math></span></span></td><td class=\"entry colname:col3\">Less than <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"delta U\"><math alttext=\"delta U\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mtext>Δ</mtext><mi>U</mi></math></span></span></td></tr><tr class=\"row\"><td class=\"entry colname:col1\">C</td><td class=\"entry colname:col2\">Less than <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"delta U\"><math alttext=\"delta U\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mtext>Δ</mtext><mi>U</mi></math></span></span></td><td class=\"entry colname:col3\">Equal to <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"delta U\"><math alttext=\"delta U\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mtext>Δ</mtext><mi>U</mi></math></span></span></td></tr><tr class=\"row\"><td class=\"entry colname:col1\">D</td><td class=\"entry colname:col2\">Less than <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"delta U\"><math alttext=\"delta U\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"